Sentencas: The effects of sintering temperature on the structural and electrochemical properties of SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-delta perovskite cathode film was investigated.
Titulo: Effects of sintering temperature on the structural and electrochemical properties of SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-δ perovskite cathode

Sentencas: For the structural properties of SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-delta film sintered at a temperature ranging from 900-1300 degrees C, changes in surface and cross-sectional microstructure were studied.
Titulo: Effects of sintering temperature on the structural and electrochemical properties of SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-δ perovskite cathode

Sentencas: Surface porosity and micro hardness were analyzed.
Titulo: Effects of sintering temperature on the structural and electrochemical properties of SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-δ perovskite cathode

Sentencas: The relationship of the structural properties with the electrical and electrochemical performances of the SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-delta film was examined.
Titulo: Effects of sintering temperature on the structural and electrochemical properties of SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-δ perovskite cathode

Sentencas: The high densification of the film sintered at 1300 degrees C led to the better electrical conductivity of 16.38 S cm(-1) than the 4.86 S cm(-1) of the film sintered at 900 degrees C at an operating temperature of 800 degrees C. For the electrochemical performance, the SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-delta film sintered at 1300 degrees C gained a low area specific resistance (ASR) value of 38.70 Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Effects of sintering temperature on the structural and electrochemical properties of SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-δ perovskite cathode

Sentencas: The ASR further decreased to 0.99 Omega cm(2) for the thicker film sintered at the same temperature.
Titulo: Effects of sintering temperature on the structural and electrochemical properties of SrFe0.5Ti0.5O3-δ perovskite cathode
